data.title: 1984) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: Ferrier St. Romain, 73, of Marksville died on October 18, 1984 at his residence. He is survived by two sons, Wallace St. Romain and Ransell St. Romain, both of Marksville; two daughters, Emma Jeansonne and Cora Laborde, both of Marksville; one sister, Mildred Novack of Arkansas; sixteen grandchildren and thirteen...
